    "description_long": "This is a sleek, low-profile sports car with a vibrant blue exterior and a streamlined, aerodynamic body. The car features a two-door coupe design, with a sharply sloped hood, compact cabin, and a short rear deck. The front end is characterized by angular headlights and a wide grille, while the rear displays dual round taillights and a subtle integrated bumper. The side profile reveals pronounced wheel arches housing large, shiny alloy wheels with a five-spoke design. The windows are tinted, and the roofline flows smoothly into the rear, emphasizing the car's sporty silhouette. Chrome accents and detailed trim add to the premium, high-performance appearance.",
